        "timestamp": "2017-11-23 23:37:06.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nDear Chris, \n\nI actually noticed that both amsterdam and release/1.3.2 branches point to the same sha1 a37fe92b5daca76aabd50ff1e6920670b30b84ee so your team should be good to use this branch now. \n\nYou are not going to need these version changes?",
